Output ts-demo.gif

Set Shell bash
Set FontFamily "DejaVu Sans Mono"
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1200
Set Height 680
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 45ms
Set Theme "Dracula"

Hide
Type "export PS1='$ '"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type "cat demo.mjs"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "node demo.mjs"
Enter
Sleep 7s
Sleep 1s
